   COXNET FOCUS 0626 VOLCANO AFTERMATH _ Four years after a volcano
left the tiny island nation of Montserrat in shambles the tenacious
people of this British territory are rebuilding their lives with an
optimism that belies the seriousness of living with a natural
disaster year after year. (Emling, Cox Washington Bureau). Art
includes 4-column color photo of man taking photos of the volcano
and 2-column photo of new houses under construction.
