<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SCOTUS-REVIEW-ART-4TAKES-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
THE JUSTICES DECIDE WHO'S IN CHARGE 
</HEADLINE>
  (The Week in Review) 
(NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For use by special arrangement
